
Ranger Help for: snare
======================

SYNTAX:      snare
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   9
BASE SP:     35 sp
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to set up a snare trap in certain areas
that have the right materials to make one. Players or NPCs that are
in the room with the Ranger at the time it is made, cannot be caught
in it, since they know about it. But, the first player or NPC that
wonders into the room will be caught in the snare. The only exception
to this, is when a Ranger enters the room, being extra adept at noting
things in the wild, Rangers can avoid snare traps. How long a player is
snared depends on how proficient the Ranger is at making it.

